  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To prospectively evaluate the long term metabolic and psychological effects of flexible
      intensive insulin therapy (FIT) courses in an unselected population of type 1 diabetic
      patients at the University of Basel Hospital. We hypothesize that both metabolic control and
      psychological parameters will improve.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
