  <eligibility>
    <study_pop>
      <textblock>
        All patients with type 1 diabetes followed at the Division of Endocrinology and
        Diabetology, University of Basel are strongly encouraged to attend the course 6 to 12
        months after having been diagnosed. The population that participates in those FIT courses
        includes patients from the University of Basel Hospital, but also patients that are
        referred from out of hospital physicians/diabetologists.
      </textblock>
    </study_pop>
    <sampling_method>Non-Probability Sample</sampling_method>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  All patients participating in 5 consecutive FIT courses that began between April 2002
             to April 2004

        Exclusion Criteria:
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
